---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Articles
description: Long-form writing on operations, automation, and the AI features that matter for service businesses.
permalink: /articles/
---

<section class="hero-lite"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="ey">What we write</div>
  <h1 class="h1">Writing from the trenches.</h1>
  <p class="lead">Longer-form pieces on operations, automation, and the AI features actually worth building. Written by operators who've done the work — not advisors selling it.</p>
</div></section>

<section class="section post-rows"><div class="wrap">

  {% if collections.articles.length > 0 %}
    {% for post in collections.articles | reverse %}
      <a class="post-row" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="post-row-meta">
          <span class="post-row-date">{{ post.date | date }}</span>
          <span class="post-row-tag">Article</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post-row-body">
          <h2 class="post-row-h">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          <span class="post-row-more">Read &#8594;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">No articles published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div></section>

<section class="band">
  <img class="band-bg" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dxzw1zwez/image/upload/c_fill,w_2000,q_auto,f_auto/v1779656080/tools_ixpkkk.jpg" alt="Work tools laid out on a surface" loading="lazy" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="se">The point</div>
    <h2 class="h2">Reading about it isn't fixing it.</h2>
    <div style="max-width:60ch">
      <p>Articles are the cheap version of what we do. The expensive version is sitting down with you, mapping how your business actually runs, and finding what's quietly costing you the most. That part starts with an Assessment — at no charge.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
